        Transaction reverse()
        Reverses the given transaction by generating counter-balancing transactions for the given transaction. The counter-balancing transactions use the transaction data in the DB, and just "flip" the side of the accounting equation for each line item.
        Returns:
        Counter-balancing Transaction
